<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF656ADAFD1590911D9ABDDB" bold="true" box="[745,922,1736,1769]" pageId="158" pageNumber="919">Distribution.</emphasis>
Malay Peninsula, lowland Borneo (most records from the N), and S 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF656ADAFD1691451D5FBC0B" box="[746,863,1820,1849]" country="Indonesia" name="Sumatera Utara" pageId="158" pageNumber="919">Sumatra</collectingRegion>
